ZombieDescription: buy brick oven pizza

Name: a` Chef Maurizio
HumanDescription: His brains will make you say a`more!
ZombieDescription: buy pizza oven

Name: Mafia Goon
HumanDescription: Hired muscle for the Pesto family business, he's not smart but who needs to be when you're as strong as a skyscraper.
ZombieDescription: He didn't have much of a brain to begin, so being a zombie doesn't change his routine much except for eating the people he's supposed to intimidate.

Name: NY Sports Fan
HumanDescription: Some would say sports fans from New York are already mindless zombies, the only difference being zombies have better manners.
ZombieDescription: Becoming a zombie was the best thing that happened to the New York sports fan, it gave him a purpose in society.

Name: Godfather
HumanDescription: The ruling Godfather of the Pesto family is very serious, he'll make you an offer you can't refuse... literally, just ask the Mafia Goon.
ZombieDescription: The zombie Godfather still rules the Pesto family with an undead fist, but just a bit less serious now that he's got a taste for brains... he can't refuse.

Name: Ditzy Mafia Girl
HumanDescription: Ditzy and oblivious to everything around her that isn't beautiful or sparkles.  Her turn-ons include strong abs and hair gel.
ZombieDescription: While still attracted to shiny objects and a taste for strong abs, she doesn't like hair gel anymore as it leaves a bad taste in her mouth.

Name: Chef Elephant
HumanDescription: He might be slow in the kitchen but he will never forget the order.
ZombieDescription: He's the head chef of this establishment, and he won't go down without a fight.

Name: Chef Donkey
HumanDescription: Although stubborn as a mule, he be a workhorse in your kitchen.
ZombieDescription: He's the head chef of this establishment, and he won't go down without a fight.

Name: Politician
HumanDescription: The Politician's budget is like his golf game. He eventually winds up in the hole.
ZombieDescription: He's running in an election for President of the Zombie Golf Club, he's perfect!

Name: Candidate
HumanDescription: The candidates moto is overpromise and under deliver. He's anything you want him to be.
ZombieDescription: The zombie candidates moto is undercook and over deliver. His favorite color is green.

Name: Governor
HumanDescription: The only difference between this governor and a pit bull is the lipstick.
ZombieDescription: There's little difference between this governor and a pit bull, except the governor has a stronger bite.

Name: Ex-Governor
HumanDescription: The ex-governor is really a machine sent back in time to ruin the state's economy.
ZombieDescription: He's continuing his public service by serving perfectly cooked pieces of the public to the public.

Name: Skeletal Bandito Chef
HumanDescription: His cooking skills are so good they can bring the dead back to life.
ZombieDescription: buy traditional estufa

Name: Skeleton Bride
HumanDescription: In her little white dress and a matching hat, she is dying to be married.
ZombieDescription: Without a ring and her groom, she is not a bride to be messed with.

Name: Skeleton Groom
HumanDescription: This hauntingly handsome groom is looking for the perfect bride.
ZombieDescription: With his new look, he is sure to make a killer move down the aisle.

Name: Calavera de Catrina
HumanDescription: The dame of death looks flashy and ready to get the party started.
ZombieDescription: She is green with a smirky grin. She is out to keep the spirit alive.

Name: Zombie Claus
HumanDescription: Here comes Zombie Claus, serving up your brains!
ZombieDescription: Here comes Zombie Claus, serving up your brains!

Name: Stir Fly Head Chef
HumanDescription: With an excellent sense of smell, he's sure to whip up the best.
ZombieDescription: With an excellent sense of smell, he's sure to whip up the best.

Name: Fish Head Monster
HumanDescription: This mythical sea creature loves to hunt in water and on land.
ZombieDescription: The seaweed green monster looks crazy hungry.

Name: Dr. Mantis Face
HumanDescription: Take two bites and call him in the morning.
ZombieDescription: The Dr. is in-sane!

Name: Mr. ?
HumanDescription: It is hard to see if he is hungry or not.
ZombieDescription: A little toxin helps him stand out in a crowd.

Name: Pink Retro Robot
HumanDescription: He is programmed to seek and eat.
ZombieDescription: Re-programmed and ready to serve.

Name: Blue Retro Robot
HumanDescription: He is programmed to seek and eat.
ZombieDescription: Re-programmed and ready to serve.

Name: Goblin Chef
HumanDescription: Trust him! This goblin can cook evilly good food.

Name: Knight in Armor
HumanDescription: In shining armor, he is trained to protect and serve.
ZombieDescription: This knight is going mental! Better keep him unarmed.

Name: Executioner
HumanDescription: He decides who will live to eat another day.
ZombieDescription: He is ready to serve your last meal.

Name: Wizard
HumanDescription: Look out when he casts a hunger spell.
ZombieDescription: His magic is now all twisted and weird!

Name: Mighty King
HumanDescription: When his belly is full, he will be ready to rule again.
ZombieDescription: "Off with his head" is this king's favorite phrase.

ZombieDescription: With a belly full of toxin, he can't wait to spit some serious fire.

Name: Evil Queen
HumanDescription: She is thirsty for the best beauty potion.
ZombieDescription: Mirror Mirror on the wall who's the fairest server of them all?

Name: Female Captain
HumanDescription: She sets sail in search of good food.
ZombieDescription: Oh Captain! My Captain! Our tasty food is done.

Name: Marooner
HumanDescription: Surviving a shipwreck is no joke but another day without food is just as bad.
ZombieDescription: He will never leave any hungry customer behind.

Name: Undead Skeleton Pirate
HumanDescription: Feed this pirate before he makes someone walk the plank.
ZombieDescription: Greets customers with a friendly "Arrr!".

Name: Shipmate
HumanDescription: This fellow shipmate reports for hungry duty.
ZombieDescription: He can swab the deck while serving the best.

Name: Conquistador
HumanDescription: Let's raid the best restaurant in town.
ZombieDescription: He rules Spain, the ocean and yes, the kitchen too.

Name: Chef Deadbeard
HumanDescription: He can hook you up with a boatload of pirate recipes.
ZombieDescription: He can hook you up with a boatload of pirate recipes.

ZombieDescription: This vampire is so old, he can't stop coffin'

Name: Vampire Hunter
HumanDescription: Slaying vampires is only good on a full stomach.

Name: Vampire Ghoul
HumanDescription: He will eat anything with a pulse.
ZombieDescription: Flying zombies, they'll revolutionize the service industry!

Name: Goth
HumanDescription: She's into black magic and disturbingly good food.
ZombieDescription: She will take blood donation as tips.

Name: Chef Dracula
HumanDescription: He can cook the most fang-tastic food.
ZombieDescription: He can cook the most fang-tastic food.

Name: Break-fast
HumanDescription: He is in search of fast food, very fast food...

Name: Shadow Skull

ZombieDescription: He may take vengeance on the low tipper.

Name: Supper girl

Name: Dr. Hoboken

Name: Galacticus

ZombieDescription: He aims to conquer your hunger and the world!
